gText_Birch_Welcome::
	.string "Hey there, I'm Professor Frank!\l"
	.string "Legally, anyway.\p"
	.string "Got the papers off some guy in a\n"
	.string "Waffle House parking lot. Long story.\p"
	.string "This here's the world of Pokémon.\p"
	.string "Some people train 'em, some people\n"
	.string "battle 'em, I just try to sell 'em\l"
	.string "when the market's hot.\p"
	.string "$"

